{"id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0001","text":"原來幾經辛苦小心抉擇都選錯","structure":{"line_index":1,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["選擇錯誤","努力白費","後悔"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["辛苦","抉擇","選錯"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,9,3,3,9,9,3,4,2,3,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyun4","loi4","gei2","ging1","san1","fu2","siu2","sam1","kyut3","zaak6","dou1","syun2","co3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"原來","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"幾經","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"辛苦","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"小心","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"抉擇","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"選錯","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"以「原來」開頭，表達一種無奈的發現，後續的「幾經辛苦小心抉擇」描述了過程的艱辛，但最終的「都選錯」卻是強烈的負面結果。"},"source":{"title":"不必多說話","artists":["張信哲"],"lyricists":["向雪懷"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2456","prev_line_id":null,"next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0002","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
