{"id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0007","text":"我應想過","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":4},"semantics":{"themes":["反思","覺悟"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["想過"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","soeng2","gwo3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我應","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"過","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"「我應想過」表示一種事後的反思和領悟，為後續的態度轉變做鋪墊。"},"source":{"title":"不必多說話","artists":["張信哲"],"lyricists":["向雪懷"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2456","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0008","text":"不必的說話 不必多說吧","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["停止溝通","無謂爭執"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["不必","說話","多說"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,4,2,3,3,3,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bat1","bit1","dik1","syut3","waa6","bat1","bit1","do1","syut3","baa6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"不必","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"說話","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不必","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"多","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"說","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"吧","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"重複的「不必說話」、「不必多說」強調了停止無謂溝通的決定，語氣帶有勸慰或自我安慰的意味。"},"source":{"title":"不必多說話","artists":["張信哲"],"lyricists":["向雪懷"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2456","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0009","text":"即使心痛知道我會懂得怎應付","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["堅強","承受能力"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["心痛","懂得","應付"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,3,4,3,2,5,9,3,9,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zik1","si2","sam1","tung3","zi1","dou6","ngo5","dung2","dak1","zam2","fu6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"即使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"心痛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"知道","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"懂得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"怎","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"應付","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「即使心痛」承認了痛苦，但「知道我會懂得怎應付」展現了內心的堅強和應對困難的能力。"},"source":{"title":"不必多說話","artists":["張信哲"],"lyricists":["向雪懷"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2456","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0010","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
