{"id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0014","text":"不要你講一句過去再義無反顧","structure":{"line_index":14,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["放下過去","不再回頭"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["不要","一句","義無反顧"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,4,5,9,3,4,4,4,4,2,0,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bat1","jiu3","nei5","gong2","jat1","geoi3","gwo3","heoi3","zoi3","ji6","mou4","faan2","gu3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"不要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"講","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一句","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"過去","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"義無反顧","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「不要你講一句過去」是明確的要求，而「再義無反顧」則表達了敘述者自己將不再回頭的決心。"},"source":{"title":"不必多說話","artists":["張信哲"],"lyricists":["向雪懷"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2456","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0013","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0015","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
