{"id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0019","text":"只要你講一切過去懂得怎應付","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["放下過去","應對能力"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["只要","講","懂得","應付"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,4,5,9,3,4,4,4,9,3,9,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zi2","jiu3","nei5","gong2","jat1","cai3","gwo3","heoi3","dung2","dak1","zam2","fu6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"只要","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"講","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一切","pos":"DET"},{"text":"過去","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"懂得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"怎","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"應付","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「只要你講一切過去」是條件，而「懂得怎應付」是敘述者能做到的，表達了即使面對過去，自己也能處理。"},"source":{"title":"不必多說話","artists":["張信哲"],"lyricists":["向雪懷"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2456","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0020","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0020","text":"不要你假惺惺吻我的傷口","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["虛偽的關心","拒絕安慰"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["不要","假惺惺","吻","傷口"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,4,5,9,3,3,5,5,3,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["bat1","jiu3","nei5","gaa2","sing1","sing1","man5","ngo5","dik1","soeng1","hau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"不要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"假惺惺","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"吻","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"傷口","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「不要你假惺惺吻我的傷口」直接拒絕了虛偽的關心和安慰，語氣強烈且帶有厭惡。"},"source":{"title":"不必多說話","artists":["張信哲"],"lyricists":["向雪懷"],"year":0,"genre":["Mandopop","Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2456","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5L-h5ZOy_MjQ1Ng_0021","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
